---
title: Caribbean-Spiced Black Bean Curry with Zesty Quinoa
description: If we had to describe our carribean spiced black bean curry in three words, it would have to be sweet, smoky and spicy. Served on a bed of zesty quinoa and sprinkled in dessicated coconut for added sweetness, this recipe will have you wishing for warmer climes!
